txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Monstrous filth from the insects near Gath Forthnír. Deilvery of the items should be made to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-outpost.
'We will find a use for this.'
'We have been told that there are uses for the filth left by the insects in the wild. Bring it to us, and we will see.'
Council of the North Task: Monstrous Filth
The Rangers at Gath Forthnír await a delivery of monstrous filth to be made to Areneth.
Deliver the monstrous filth to Areneth at Gath Forthnír in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver monstrous filth from the insects near Gath Forthnír to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-camp.
Wanted: Monstrous filth from the insects near Gath Forthnír.
